[
  {
    "startTime": 1.725,
    "endTime": 3.101,
    "text": "What is that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.977,
    "endTime": 4.853,
    "text": "Uh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.022,
    "endTime": 10.484,
    "text": "It-- It's the speech Hop wrote for you and Mike."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.026,
    "endTime": 11.985,
    "text": "Speech?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.402,
    "endTime": 14.613,
    "text": "Yeah. You know, the heart-to-heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.783,
    "endTime": 19.743000000000002,
    "text": "He never talked to you, did he?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.661,
    "endTime": 22.704,
    "text": "[scoffs]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.457,
    "endTime": 26.666,
    "text": "Can I read?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.762,
    "endTime": 41.973,
    "text": "[Hopper] \"There's something I've been wanting to talk to you both about."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.6,
    "endTime": 45.811,
    "text": "I know this is a difficult conversation,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.894,
    "endTime": 48.647,
    "text": "but I care about you both very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.356,
    "endTime": 51.858000000000004,
    "text": "And I know that you care about each other very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.942,
    "endTime": 55.612,
    "text": "And that's why it's important that we set these boundaries moving forward,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.695,
    "endTime": 57.781,
    "text": "so we can build an environment..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.326,
    "endTime": 63.286,
    "text": "where we all feel..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.913,
    "endTime": 66.289,
    "text": "comfortable..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.999,
    "endTime": 69.167,
    "text": "trusted..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.794,
    "endTime": 72.003,
    "text": "and open..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.506,
    "endTime": 76.591,
    "text": "to sharing our feelings.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.93,
    "endTime": 83.05600000000001,
    "text": "Feelings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.146,
    "endTime": 90.147,
    "text": "[murmurs]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.11,
    "endTime": 96.236,
    "text": "[Hopper] Feelings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.904,
    "endTime": 99.072,
    "text": "Jesus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.281,
    "endTime": 100.15700000000001,
    "text": "[chuckles]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.657,
    "endTime": 102.033,
    "text": "The truth is,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.368,
    "endTime": 106.83,
    "text": "for so long, I'd forgotten what those even were."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.415,
    "endTime": 110.417,
    "text": "I've been stuck in one place,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.959,
    "endTime": 112.62700000000001,
    "text": "in a cave, you might say."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.253,
    "endTime": 114.88,
    "text": "A deep, dark cave."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.881,
    "endTime": 118.925,
    "text": "And then, I left some Eggos out in the woods,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.009,
    "endTime": 121.094,
    "text": "and you came into my life and..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.887,
    "endTime": 125.015,
    "text": "for the first time in a long time,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.309,
    "endTime": 129.478,
    "text": "I started to feel things again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.604,
    "endTime": 132.52200000000002,
    "text": "I started to feel happy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.735,
    "endTime": 139.69600000000003,
    "text": "But, lately, I guess I've been feeling..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.49,
    "endTime": 142.824,
    "text": "distant from you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.201,
    "endTime": 145.243,
    "text": "Like you're..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.453,
    "endTime": 148.538,
    "text": "you're pulling away from me or something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.581,
    "endTime": 151.833,
    "text": "I miss playing board games every night,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.543,
    "endTime": 157.506,
    "text": "making triple-decker Eggo extravaganzas at sunrise,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.089,
    "endTime": 160.8,
    "text": "watching westerns together before we doze off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.594,
    "endTime": 164.221,
    "text": "But I know you're getting older."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.68,
    "endTime": 166.848,
    "text": "Growing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.641,
    "endTime": 168.767,
    "text": "Changing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.393,
    "endTime": 171.603,
    "text": "And I guess..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.896,
    "endTime": 174.356,
    "text": "if I'm being really honest,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.357,
    "endTime": 176.733,
    "text": "that's what scares me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.902,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "I don't want things to change."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.95,
    "endTime": 187.244,
    "text": "So, I think maybe that's why I came in here,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.327,
    "endTime": 190.49699999999999,
    "text": "to try to maybe... stop that change."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.332,
    "endTime": 193.917,
    "text": "To turn back the clock."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.918,
    "endTime": 198.088,
    "text": "To make things go back to how they were."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.381,
    "endTime": 201.675,
    "text": "[Hopper sighs deeply]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.009,
    "endTime": 204.594,
    "text": "But I know that's naive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.554,
    "endTime": 206.471,
    "text": "It's just..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.681,
    "endTime": 209.09900000000002,
    "text": "not how life works."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.933,
    "endTime": 211.184,
    "text": "It's moving."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.977,
    "endTime": 214.479,
    "text": "Always moving, whether you like it or not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.398,
    "endTime": 219.651,
    "text": "And, yeah, sometimes it's painful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.944,
    "endTime": 222.279,
    "text": "Sometimes it's sad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.822,
    "endTime": 225.323,
    "text": "And sometimes..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.449,
    "endTime": 227.86700000000002,
    "text": "it's surprising."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.369,
    "endTime": 230.328,
    "text": "Happy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.747,
    "endTime": 233.83200000000002,
    "text": "So, you know what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.958,
    "endTime": 236.167,
    "text": "Keep on growing up, kid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.335,
    "endTime": 238.87800000000001,
    "text": "Don't let me stop you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.838,
    "endTime": 242.465,
    "text": "Make mistakes, learn from 'em,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.383,
    "endTime": 246.38600000000002,
    "text": "and when life hurts you, because it will,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.387,
    "endTime": 248.805,
    "text": "remember the hurt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.806,
    "endTime": 252.51700000000002,
    "text": "The hurt is good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.226,
    "endTime": 255.645,
    "text": "It means you're out of that cave."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.981,
    "endTime": 259.565,
    "text": "But, please,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.399,
    "endTime": 262.027,
    "text": "if you don't mind,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.986,
    "endTime": 265.53,
    "text": "for the sake of your poor old dad,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.364,
    "endTime": 270.284,
    "text": "keep the door open three inches."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.368,
    "endTime": 271.411,
    "text": "[laughs]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.288,
    "endTime": 274.456,
    "text": "[sniffles]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.082,
    "endTime": 276.916,
    "text": "[sobs]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.0,
    "endTime": 279.002,
    "text": "[\"Heroes\" by Peter Gabriel playing]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.336,
    "endTime": 281.087,
    "text": "♪ I ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.548,
    "endTime": 285.133,
    "text": "♪ I will be king... ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.176,
    "endTime": 287.426,
    "text": "[knocking on door]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.387,
    "endTime": 290.764,
    "text": "Are you okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.267,
    "endTime": 295.185,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.729,
    "endTime": 298.772,
    "text": "[sniffles]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.272,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "Time to go?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.025,
    "endTime": 303.109,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.027,
    "endTime": 305.82,
    "text": "I'll be out in a minute."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.155,
    "endTime": 308.239,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.574,
    "endTime": 311.701,
    "text": "♪ Oh, we could be heroes ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.413,
    "endTime": 317.165,
    "text": "♪ Just for one day ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.251,
    "endTime": 322.253,
    "text": "♪ Oh, we can be us ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.674,
    "endTime": 327.842,
    "text": "♪ Just for one day ♪"
  }
]